<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
我這身服裝！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />沒錯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
我就是被施展了名為「復活節」魔法的，<delay20 />
高興得不得了的<tag a="110" b="15" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />也看到了嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />那輕快的舞步<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可不是等閒之輩跳得出來的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />他配合著拍子跳啊跳的，<delay20 />
輕巧的步伐讓人感受不到絲毫重力<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
簡直就像是沒有穿衣服似的<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節的蛋<delay20 />
其實是可以吃的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，竟然要吃掉<delay20 />
猶如藝術品般美麗的蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
真的有點不忍心啊～</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你要記得抬頭看看天空喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為時不時會有彩色的氣球飛過呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有東西<delay20 />
可以把氣球射下來就好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說，你熱情的視線！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />開玩笑的啦，哈哈！</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在海邊散步的時候，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />找到一個色彩繽紛的瓶中信，<delay20 />
還以為是復活節的蛋呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然不知道把它放到海中的人在想什麼，<delay20 />
不過湊巧的是，它在復活節這一天<delay20 />
漂流到了<tag a="110" b="8" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />你也覺得吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這正是<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節的奇蹟啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />也看到了嗎？<10_4 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不可思議的蛋<delay20 />
正在<tag a="110" b="8" />的天空中飄著<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經不覺得有什麼好驚訝的了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難道我也被施了魔法嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是那名為「復活節」的魔法<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個，<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛才搖了一下眼前的樹，<delay20 />
突然有一顆彩色的蛋掉了下來。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我嚇了一跳，但同時也相信……<delay frames="40" />
這就是復活節<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />送我的禮物，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我剛剛釣魚釣得正開心的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然釣到了一個特別的東西，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />本以為這是花紋美麗的魚<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />誰知道竟然是蛋！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這就是Easter Magic吧。</message>
</msbt>